node.text: Watch how Melvin Gravely, CEO of TriVersity Construction -- the largest minority contractor in the history of Cincinnati -- believes it’s his duty to reinvest in the community to ensure diversity and equal opportunity. He currently sits on P&G’s Supplier Diversity Advisory Council.  Visit our #LinkInBio for more about our commitment to Black-owned businesses.
Believe in yourself and focus on your goal,take risk ,I took the risk ,he has really been a wonderful account manager to me @paidlikejonny

shortcode_media.title: Black Business Month: TriVersity Construction – Growing Diverse Talent
